title: 이달의소녀탐구 #345 (LOONA TV #345)
members: Olivia Hye, Go Won, Chuu, Yves
summary:
0:08 -- Go Won blows a dandelion. "Oh~ You~". Hye: "I guess she doesn't like me" as all the petals hit her.
0:18 -- Olivia tries blowing one but fails. Chuu tries and the petals flee. She goes crazy and blows many more affecting the makeup.
0:49 -- Chuuves blow more dandelions as a part of the photoshoot.
